# Master Blueprint: Schema (Sincronizado)

## Tables & Fields

### Roles
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `nombre` (String, Unique)

### Privilegios
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `ref_modulo` (String)
- `read` (Boolean)
- `write` (Boolean)
- `exec` (Boolean)
- `role_id` (FK -> Roles.id)

### Users
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `nombre` (String)
- `email` (String, Unique)
- `password` (String)
- `role_id` (FK -> Roles.id)

### Tools
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `nombre` (String)
- `descripcion` (Text)
- `logo_herramienta` (String)
- `training_prompt` (Text)
- `behavior_prompt` (Text)
- `response_format` (String)
- `output_format_id` (FK -> OutputFormats.id)
- `json_schema_id` (FK -> JsonSchemas.id)

### JsonSchemas
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `nombre` (String)
- `descripcion` (Text)
- `schema` (Text - JSON Schema)

### OutputCategories
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `nombre` (String, Unique)

### OutputFormats
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `nombre` (String)
- `tipo` (Enum: reporte, accionable, generativo)
- `estructura` (Text - JSON/HTML template)
- `category_id` (FK -> OutputCategories.id)

### Configs
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `key` (String, Unique)
- `value` (Text)

### Engines
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `nombre` (String)
- `slug` (String, Unique)
- `descripcion` (Text)
- `tipo` (Enum: iterator, collector, mapper)
- `icono` (String)
- `config_schema` (Text - JSON)
- `activo` (Boolean)

### Machines
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `nombre` (String)
- `descripcion` (Text)
- `icono` (String)
- `activo` (Boolean)

### MachineNodes
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `machine_id` (FK -> Machines.id)
- `node_type` (Enum: tool, engine)
- `tool_id` (FK -> Tools.id, nullable)
- `engine_id` (FK -> Engines.id, nullable)
- `position_x` (Float)
- `position_y` (Float)
- `config` (Text - JSON)

### MachineConnections
- `id` (UUID, PK)
- `machine_id` (FK -> Machines.id)
- `source_node_id` (FK -> MachineNodes.id)
- `target_node_id` (FK -> MachineNodes.id)
- `source_handle` (String)
- `target_handle` (String)
